long_description:
Appian Connected Claims is a suite of integrated, modular applications that support and streamline the entire claims lifecycle, from first notice of loss, to payment, closure, and reporting. The solution enables P&C and Life insurers
deliver a 360-degree view of each claim in an actionable dashboard, unifying data from all systems, and third-party applications without data migration, optimize claim handling with intelligent automation and reduce time and cost to implement.

Choose one or all modules of the Connected Claims solution to address an insurers unique needs:
Customer Service;
Claim Operations and Settlement;
Fraud Case Management;
First Notice of Loss (FNOL);
Litigation and Recovery Management;
-Continuous Improvement Analysis
Field Inspections
-Loss Intake

Contact us at aws-marketplace@appian.com for more information on pricing or a tailored solution via Private Offer.
